<?xml version="1.0" encoding="utf-8"?>
<Subtitle>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>1</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>11609</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>20562</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>国王在照镜子。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>2</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>20562</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>26140</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他在转身时吓了一跳。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>3</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>26140</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>31468</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“萨尔，快进来！” 国王大喊。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>4</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>31468</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>39038</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>仆人赶紧跑进来。“陛下，怎么了?”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>5</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>39038</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>46517</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我的袍子上有一根头发。” 国王说，“我拿不到。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>6</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>46517</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>50880</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>仆人拿到了头发。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>7</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>50880</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>54130</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“谢谢。” 国王说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>8</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>54130</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>60150</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我是国王。我的袍子上是不能有头发的！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>9</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>60150</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>67252</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>国王往下看。“萨尔，你的鞋带没系好。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>10</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>67252</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>75145</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>萨尔赶紧系好鞋带。“抱歉，陛下。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>11</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>75145</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>86114</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>国王坐在王座上。人们等着见他。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>12</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>86114</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>90653</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>仆人一次让一个人进去。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>13</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>90653</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>94880</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>首先，一个女人走了进来。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>14</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>94880</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>100177</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“陛下，我要找工作。” 她说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>15</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>100177</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>103458</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我会做针线活。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>16</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>103458</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>107857</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>她的头发垂到脸上。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>17</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>107857</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>113216</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>国王给了女人一个工作。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>18</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>113216</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>118210</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>还给了她一条发带。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>19</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>118210</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>123787</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>接着，一个男人走了进来。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>20</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>123787</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>129498</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他的裤子太大了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>21</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>129498</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>134005</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我的邻居们很穷。” 男人说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>22</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>134005</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>138086</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“他们又老又饿。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>23</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>138086</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>143969</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“带点食物给你的邻居。” 国王说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>24</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>143969</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>146821</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他看向仆人。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>25</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>146821</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>157592</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“给他一条腰带！” 国王大喊。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>26</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>157592</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>163818</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>国王皱着眉头看着男人离开。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>27</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>163818</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>168318</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“大家都不太整洁。” 他想。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>28</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>168318</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>171777</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>门又开了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>29</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>171777</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>182219</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>一只穿着华丽靴子的猫走了进来！</Text>
  </Paragraph>
</Subtitle>